CSO 

  [Text] Police antinarcotics officials seized 605 kg of 
opium in Shiraz, Darab, Lamard, and Nayriz in Fars Province. 
  The Fars Police Precinct public relations official said on 
Saturday: This opium was seized during the last few days from 
passing vehicles, and the distribution agents were identified. 
  According to him, several of the primary defendants involved 
in distributing the opium were arrested and turned over to 
judicial officials. 

